---
title: Thai Spiced Turkey Mince Udon with scallion and bell peppers
description: The turkey mince in this recipe is seasoned with a beautiful blend of Thai-inspired spices. Paired with crunchy bell peppers and thick tasty udon noodles, this is a quick and simple meal with lots of flavour.
